{"type": "article", "id": 16564, "title": "翻转雨伞", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-26T06:51:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 74, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135542b75Or32tXSa6ocLg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一把翻转伞，它的伞面是反向的，如果只是稍微淋过雨的雨伞，雨水就完全收在伞里而不会滴出来。它更特别之处在于弯曲的手把可以拆解下来双向安装，因而当雨伞淋过大雨或需要滴水的时候，就可以拆下来装在另一头让它自然滴落。设计者是为了解决雨伞到处滴水，导致地面过去潮湿的问题，这把翻转伞让滴水变得可控。产品目前在众筹，有蓝色和紫色两款，<a href=\"http://www.zeczec.com/projects/iumbrella\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143759j5vFU6VtdJcwlHzy.jpg\" width=\"532\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5037594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143759kpeHfXT7NWSFogi4.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"469\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79491525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143800uHMV6cphjOnsr8kX.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"722\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.9025\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143800ls78w2ryopuLSAvt.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"792\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.99\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}